        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "### Request audit contract\nOpen a matching trace and select the `litellm_request` span. The same span contains its UTC start time, `aigw.user.id`, `aigw.project.id`, `aigw.api_key.id` (SHA-256 fingerprint only), `aigw.request.id`, and the approved `gen_ai.input.messages` / `gen_ai.output.messages` content. Raw authorization, API keys, request headers, email, IP, and unfiltered LiteLLM auth metadata are removed before Tempo or Cribl export. Prompt content is sensitive and this dashboard is intentionally ADM-only.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.5",
      "title": "How to inspect a request",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "tempo",
        "uid": "tempo"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 14,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "countRows": false,
          "fields": "",
          "reducer": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "show": false
        },
        "showHeader": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.5",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "tempo",
            "uid": "tempo"
          },
          "limit": 100,
          "query": "{ span:name = \"litellm_request\" && span.aigw.user.id != nil && span.aigw.project.id != nil && span.aigw.api_key.id != nil } | select(span.aigw.user.id, span.aigw.project.id, span.aigw.api_key.id, span.aigw.request.id, span.gen_ai.input.messages, span.gen_ai.output.messages) with (most_recent=true)",
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "refId": "A",
          "spanLimit": 20,
          "tableType": "spans"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Fully Correlated AI Requests",
      "type": "table"
    },
